metadata.name: Bunny Hut #1
metadata.description: This series promulgates the profound theses of: • Kitty • Bunny • Puppy (inside →) • Lovely cottage • Inviting sky • Fluffy cloud • Bright bright sun, or → • Happy moon  • All the constellations in the universe • Lawn that never needs mowing • Sidewalk that never trips • Window shades revealing more than they hide • Welcoming, informative sign • Door with no lock • All the color needed, or none (when needed) • [PNG 5832 x 5631 pixels]
